---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SiteNav from '../components/SiteNav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer';
---

<Layout
  title="Private AI Support & Success"
  description="Understand the white-glove onboarding, monitoring, and ongoing optimization included with intent solutions io deployments."
>
  <SiteNav />

  <main class="bg-zinc-900">
    <section class="py-24 border-b border-zinc-800/60">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-8">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <p class="uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 mb-4">
            support
          </p>
          <h1 class="text-h1 font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-6">
            White-glove support from kickoff through scale
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
            Private AI adoption is a journey. We partner with your teams using hands-on onboarding, 24/7 monitoring, and proactive
            optimization reviews so the platform stays reliable and operators stay confident.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 bg-zinc-950 border-b border-zinc-800/60">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-10">Support fundamentals</h2>
        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">White-glove onboarding</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              Guided rollout, team training, and documentation customized for your playbooks ensure day-one adoption.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">24/7 monitoring</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              Automated health checks and on-call engineers keep availability on track around the clock.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Guaranteed response</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              4-hour standard SLA and 1-hour enterprise SLA for critical incidents, communicated via your preferred channels.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Monthly reviews</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              Optimization sessions walk through usage trends, backlog priorities, and roadmap adjustments.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Shared tooling</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              Ticketing, alerting, and dashboards live in shared portals so you have the same visibility we do.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Change management</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              Structured comms plans, stakeholder briefings, and release notes keep leadership and operators aligned.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 border-b border-zinc-800/60">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-8">
        <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 items-start">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-6">Onboarding timeline</h2>
            <ol class="space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-300 list-decimal list-inside">
              <li>Kickoff workshop to align goals, success metrics, and rollout teams.</li>
              <li>Hands-on configuration sessions covering infrastructure, models, and integrations.</li>
              <li>Role-based enablement training with live exercises and certification checklists.</li>
              <li>Launch support window with office hours and rapid iteration on feedback.</li>
            </ol>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mt-4">
              You receive playbooks, recorded sessions, and quick-reference guides so future hires can onboard with minimal friction.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate space-y-4">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-50">Support channels</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-300">
              <li>Dedicated Slack or Teams channel with direct engineer access.</li>
              <li>Ticket queue integrated with Jira, Linear, or your ITSM platform.</li>
              <li>Emergency hotline for severity one incidents when minutes matter.</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500">
              Prefer a different workflow? We adapt to email, SMS, or PagerDuty based on your escalation policies.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 bg-zinc-950 border-b border-zinc-800/60">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-6">Continuous improvement</h2>
        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Usage analytics</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              Dashboards highlight adoption, satisfaction, and agent performance so we can prioritize the right enhancements.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Prompt and policy tuning</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              Monthly review cycles refine prompts, guardrails, and automations based on real user conversations.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Cost governance</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              Spending reports and forecasting models keep GPU, storage, and data transfer costs predictable.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Innovation backlog</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              Joint roadmap planning sessions capture new features, integrations, and experiments to tackle next.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-8">
        <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-4">Meet the team behind your success plan</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mb-6">
              We introduce the engineers, analysts, and program leads supporting your account so you know exactly who to call.
            </p>
            <a href="/#contact" class="btn-primary">Start your onboarding conversation</a>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate space-y-4">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-50">Common questions</h3>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-300 font-medium">Do you cover nights and weekends?</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">Yes. Our monitoring and on-call rotations run 24/7 with the agreed SLA windows.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-300 font-medium">Can we include our partners?</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">We will onboard MSPs, franchise operators, or vendors under your guidance with tailored permissions.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-300 font-medium">What happens after the first year?</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">We renew support scopes annually, adjusting coverage as usage expands across teams and regions.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
